titleInfo.title: (PC) Bartholomew v. Moore, et al
titleInfo.subTitle: FINDINGS and RECOMMENDATIONS signed by Magistrate Judge Carolyn K. Delaney on 1/26/2012 RECOMMENDING that defendant Lane and Cheser's 21 motion for summary judgment be denied with the respect to plaintiff's claim that defendants Cheser and Lane violated plaintiff's rights arising under the First Amendment by retaliating against plaintiff for pursing an inmate grievance, and granted in all other respects; plaintiff be ordered to file his pretrial statement within 30 daysof any order adopting these findings and recommendations, and defendants be ordered to file their pretrial statement within 21 days of service of plaintiff's pretrial statement. Referred to Judge Kimberly J. Mueller; Objections due within 21 days. (Yin, K)
